Unilever sale plan may affect India unit . The Anglo - Dutch food and personal products group Unilever Plc ' s announcement that it intends to sell its international speciality chemicals business may impact the Hindustan Lever Ltd , the Indian subsidiary said . " I have just come to learn from Unilever ' s announcement that it intends to sell its international speciality chemicals business - - National Starch & Chemicals Co , Quest International , Unichema International and Crosfield - - as part of the strategic development of its portfolio , " Hindustan Lever chairman K . B . Dadiseth said in a statement on Tuesday . " Many of the product categories of these companies are represented within Hindustan Lever Ltd , " it said . " The board of Hindustan Lever will consider the impact of this decision on its Indian operations in due course , " it said . 
